data.text:
The FASE designation recognizes dedicated ASE members with proven professional contributions, diverse sets of skills, and knowledge of all aspects of cardiovascular ultrasound. Listed below are the highly certified practitioners who have achieved this title. The glossary allows you to search this outstanding group of cardiovascular ultrasound professionals by US state. Learn more about the FASE designation at ASEcho.org/FASE.

To search by state, click state abbreviation below.
